data.text: @RealCandaceO BLACKOUT. The title alone says it all. How you shape your life. Don’t take my comment out of context. Interracial couples MARRY BECAUSE THEY LOVE EACH OTHER! They do. But in your specific case, it’s to have no reminders of “us,” even when U go home.
